Damage (ranged): 1d4+3 (acid)
Speed Factor: 1
Proficiency Type: Dagger
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 3 Strength

Weight: 1
~
@1081 = ~Robe~
@1082 = ~Wyrd's Ended Slumber~
@1083 = ~This robe is known as wyrd's Ended Slumber and it won't be very surprising to say that it was once used by a wyrd from Myth Unnohyr. It feels like it might have looked similar to one of the robes of archimagi, but it was clearly warped by time and wyrd's influence. 

