– Magic Resistance: +5%
– Caster level (arcane): +4

Weight: 6
~
@1084 = ~Staff~
@1085 = ~Branch from the Duskwood Dell +3~
@1086 = ~This quarstaff is a powerful weapon, created for those value balance and life. There still grean leaves grow from it, and while it's somewhat less efficient in fighting than other weapons of this enchantment, it has powerful healing properties.

There are some symbols cut on the branch, which indicates that this weapon has been created as a tribute to Eldath. 

