@1093 = ~Thornshooter +1~
@1094 = ~This crossbow can shoot its own magical thorns that are able to entangle the target.
  
The magic used to create this weapon, however, makes only singleclass druid use this crossbow.
  
STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
